INSERT INTO `ext_organization` (`id`, `gid`, `name`, `size_id`, `type_id`, `country_id`, `collaboration`, `transaction`, `website`, `description`, `specialties`) VALUES
(29, 24, 'Cybion Srl', 'B', 'C', 'IT', 1, 1, 'cybion.it', 'Cybion Srl', 'Cybion Srl'),
(30, 25, 'Diatheva srl', 'C', 'P', 'IT', 1, 0, 'http://www.diatheva.com', 'DIATHEVA is an Italian biotech company founded in 2002 with the aim to bring research into industrial products by cooperating with firms, public and private research institutions.DIATHEVA focuses on development, production and marketing of new and innovative products (antibodies, recombinant proteins, immunoassays and SNPs detection kits) for diagnostics, research and therapeutic applications in the field of: Cancer, Microbial Infection and Pharmacogenetics.DIATHEVA has a GMP authorized facility designed for the manufacture of APIs for pre-clinical and clinical trial studies with a special emphasis on new immunogens against HIV and other microbial pathogens. DIATHEVA is the first facility in Italy able to provides GMP service on-demand. From 2009 DIATHEVA has been a member of Marche BIOTECH and has been collaborating with the most important biotechnological companies in the Marche region extending its scientific network.From 2010 DIATHEVA has been providing a wide range of pharmacogenetic tests for personalized and predictive medicine based on High Resolution Melting technologies with priority focused on anti-tumoral treatments.', 'Microbiology,DNA Technology,Cell Biology,Genetic Diseases,Tumor Markers,SNPs & Genotyping'),
(31, 26, 'Microsoft', 'I', 'C', 'AF', 1, 1, 'http://www.microsoft.com/', 'Come as you are. Do what you love. At Microsoft we help people and businesses throughout the world realize their full potential. We make this simple mission come to life every day through our passion to create technologies and develop products that touch just about every kind of customer. Working at Microsoft gives you the opportunity to do things that make a real difference in millions, even billions, of lives. To reach your full potential. So why not take a closer look at Microsoft? We think you’ll find that amazing things really do happen here.', 'Business Software,Design Tools,Developer Tools,Entertainment Products,Hardware,Home & Educational Software,Mobile Devices & Software,Search,Advertising,Servers,Windows Operating System,Windows Applications & Platforms,Windows Live,Cloud Computing'),
(33, 28, 'LGC Genomics', 'D', 'P', 'CA', 1, 1, 'www.lgcgenomics.com', 'LGC Genomics (www.lgcgenomics.com) is the genomics division of the international science-based LGC Group. Last year LGC Genomics merged with KBioscience, a UK-based technology company providing its own range of SNP genotyping chemistry and novel instrumentation to the life science research and quality control communities. The combined company provides a full range of high quality genomics products, services and solutions including, sample preparation (primarily, nucleic acid extraction), nucleic acid sequencing, genotyping and biobanking. LGC Genomics has laboratories in the UK, Germany and North America along with sales and support staff in over 15 locations in Europe, America and the Far East.The portfolio includes:- Genotyping services, assays and reagents- DNA sequencing services including NextGen sequencing services on both the Roche 454 & Illumina HiSeq2000 platforms- DNA and RNA extraction products and services- DNA/RNA biobanking including, storage, retrieval and analysis services- Reagents and consumables for molecular biology- Pharmacogenetics and diagnostic services- Laboratory instrumentation including plate sealers, liquid handling robots, high-throughput PCR thermocyclers, plate readers and a suite of laboratory automation instruments', 'DNA sequencing,DNA Extraction,Genotyping,Instruments and software,Laboratory services,Biobanking,Reagents and consumables,NextGen sequencing'),
(34, 29, 'micEnterprise', 'D', 'P', 'IT', 1, 0, 'www.mic-enterprise.com', 'company developing medical chemical components and performing research on genetics', 'chemistry, genetics'),
(35, 30, 'Cybion Srl', 'B', 'P', 'IT', 1, 0, 'http://www.cybion.it', 'Since 1995 Cybion supports companies and public institutions in web monitoring, analysis and online reputation management activities, combining innovative technology and analysis experience. Cybion focuses on various sectors, such as environment and sustainable development, high tech, foods and beverage, cosmetics, automotive, luxury goods, defence. Cybion is currently carrying out important projects focused on online media and user interaction, by designing specific 2.0 marketing online tools, also in the participative journalism sector; setting up innovative online communication tools; defining 2.0 marketing strategy for the following industries: Food, Beverage&Tobacco, Beauty and Healthcare; developing cutting edge technologies able to support online reputation monitoring and management services. Moreover, during its participation to EU projects, Cybion contribution has often focused on the online dissemination activities: web site and portal, newslettering, realization and management of platform, and search engine and 2.0 marketing strategies', 'Web Monitoring,Brand Reputation Analysis'),
(36, 31, 'Jozef Stefan Institute', 'F', 'D', 'SI', 1, 0, 'http://www.ijs.si', 'The Jožef Stefan Institute is the leading Slovenian scientific research institute, covering a broad spectrum of basic and applied research. The staff of more than 850 specializes in natural sciences, life sciences and engineering.The subjects concern production and control technologies, communication and computer technologies, knowledge technologies, biotechnologies, new materials, environmental technologies, nanotechnologies, and nuclear engineering.The mission of the Jožef Stefan Institute is the accumulation - and dissemination - of knowledge at the frontiers of natural science and technology to the benefit of society at large through the pursuit of education, learning, research, and development of high technology at the highest international levels of excellence.', ''),
(37, 32, 'Innova', 'C', 'P', 'IT', 1, 1, 'www.innova.it', 'Company dedicated to EU projects', 'R&D'),
(38, 33, 'Festerna Srl', 'A', 'O', 'IT', 1, 0, '', 'Safety ', 'Training on Safety'),
(39, 34, 'Asemantics', 'B', 'O', 'IT', 1, 1, '', 'computer science applied to life science', 'bioinformatics'),
(40, 35, 'Asemantics', 'B', 'O', 'IT', 1, 1, '', 'Computer science applied to life science', 'bioinformatics'),
(41, 36, 'Labor Advocaten', 'B', 'S', 'NL', 1, 1, 'www.labor-advocaten.nl', 'Labor Advocaten is een gerenommeerd advocatenkantoor en uitsluitend gespecialiseerd in het arbeidsrecht en arbeidsrecht mediations. Labor Advocaten richt zich op ondernemingen, werknemers en staat ook ondernemingsraden bij. Labor Advocaten is opgericht in 2005 en gevestigd in Zeist. De focus van Labor Advocaten is niet alleen regionaal georiënteerd (Utrechtse Heuvelrug, Utrecht en Amersfoort en omgeving) ook elders uit het land weet men ons in toenemende mate te vinden. Wij werken vanuit een vertrouwensrelatie op gelijkwaardige wijze samen met onze klanten aan hun zaken. Op deze manier onderscheiden wij ons van andere kantoren. Zeker in combinatie met ons specialisme, de korte lijnen, de duidelijke en heldere manier van communiceren en onze scherpe en creatieve prijsstelling. Zo werkt Labor al sinds haar oprichting vaak met vaste prijsafspraken waardoor de klant vooraf weet waar hij aan toe is.Door de jarenlange ervaring van de advocaten en medewerkers van Labor in het arbeidsrecht en de direct aangrenzende rechtsgebieden (ondernemingsrecht, sociaal zekerheidsrecht) zijn onze klanten dan ook verzekerd van parate, specialistische kennis en een autoriteit op het gebied van het arbeidsrecht. Een van de partners van Labor Advocaten is tevens jarenlang werkzaam geweest als advocaat en HR Manager binnen grote verzekeraars. Daarmee weten wij als geen ander wat ondernemingen vragen van juridische dienstverleners en heeft Labor tevens kennis van organisatie- en veranderprocessen. Hierdoor kunnen wij onze klanten nog beter tot dienst zijn. Of het nu gaat om een ontslagkwestie, reorganisatie, opstellen dan wel wijzigen van overeenkomsten/arbeidsvoorwaarden, een bedrijfsovername of bijvoorbeeld een conflict over een concurrentiebeding: onze klanten kunnen er altijd op rekenen dat wij samen met hen zoeken naar passende en doeltreffende oplossingen tegen een eerlijk tarief passend bij de aard en spoedeisendheid van de kwestie.', 'arbeidsrecht,ontslagrecht,mediation,reorganisatie,ontslagvergoeding,bedrijfsovername,concurrentiebeding,arbeidsongeschiktheid,overgang van onderneming'),
(42, 37, 'EPIC Litho', 'D', 'P', 'IT', 1, 0, 'www.epiclitho.com', 'For more than 30 years, EPIC Litho has been listening to and anticipating the needs of organizations like yours.In the past, this meant providing traditionally printed products, but today, our services include a host of marketing innovations—including high-definition ultraviolet printing, digital printing, direct mail, online solutions, large format printing, warehousing and fulfillment, and advertising specialties.In 2012 EPIC Litho won 6 Best of Categories in the Philadelphia Graphic Arts Neo-Graphics competition.  We went on to win 2 Best of Categories in the Premier Print Awards, a national print competition run by the Printing Industries of America and a Gold Ink Award run by NAPCO.In July of 2012, we installed a new Komori GL840p HUV press, the first of its kind in the mid-Atlantic region.', 'High Defintion UV Printing'),
(43, 38, 'Benetton', 'G', 'P', 'IT', 1, 1, 'www.benetton.com', 'UCB ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------', ''),
(44, 39, 'SKD Distribution', 'A', 'S', 'PL', 1, 1, 'www.skdpolska.pl', 'Jeste?my wy??cznym dystrybutorem profesjonalnych kosmetyków fryzjerskich marek JOICO, PAUL MITCHELL, SENSCIENCE, ISO, ICE, TAIFF na terenie Polski. S? to marki rozpoznawalne w profesjonalnym ?wiecie fryzjerskim. Wspó?pracujemy z salonami dostarczaj?c produkty najwy?szej jako?ci oraz wiedz? dotycz?c? ich u?ycia. Dzia?aj?c w bran?y fryzjerskiej obserwujemy stale zmieniaj?cy si? ?wiat mody oraz tworzymy nowe trendy. Wprowadzamy nowe kolekcje i szkolimy naszych klientów.Professional Products: Portfolio of brands that meet the requirements of hair salons (JOICO, Senscience, ISO, ICE, Paul Mitchell, Taiff)) Joico, a fast-growing company in the Professional Beauty industry, is a division of Zotos/Shiseido.Our Mission:We eat, sleep and breathe beauty! We develop innovative, top performing products. We design artistic imagery that inspires creativity. We surround ourselves with the most gifted artists and educators in the industry. We are 100% committed to the advancement of the global salon community. Why? Because beauty isn’t our job—it’s our passion!', 'distribution,educating,cooperation with beauty salons');
