(87, 1, '2014-07-07 11:24:01', '2014-07-07 11:24:01', 'The LifeSienceRoom platform is the result of the Central Community project.\n\nCentralCommunity project aims at developing conditions for the creation of communities supporting each phase of the innovation process, mainly by providing SMEs with an ICT operational platform.\n\nLifeSienceRoom is a web 2.0 platform with advanced functionalities enhancing SMEs specific innovative abilities in generating and\ndesigning new ideas, trends, concepts and models about products and processes; in creating self-organized communities which support development of new products by means of a collective intelligence sharing web-applications.\n\nThe platform is customised according to the needs of Central Europe industry environment and focuses on the sectorial cluster of life sciences.\n\nThe aim of CentralCommunity project is piloting and testing LifeSienceRoom in real conditions in the context of Central European innovation players to support eco-sustainable innovation.\n\nThe project is funded under the Central Europe programme and co-financed by the ERDF.\n\nClick here for more info on Central Community.', 'About LifeSienceRoom', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '61-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-07 11:24:01', '2014-07-07 11:24:01', '', 61, 'http://gaia.cybion.eu/cecommunity/61-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
